#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:4
msgid "Input Devices"
msgstr "输入设备"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:6
msgid "Blender supports various types of input devices:"
msgstr "Blender的界面使用针对下面推荐的配置设计: "

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:8
msgid ""
"Keyboard (recommended: keyboard with numeric keypad, english layout works "
"best)"
msgstr "键盘（推荐带数字键小键盘的，英语布局键盘最好。）"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:9
msgid "Mouse (recommended: 3 button mouse with scroll wheel)"
msgstr "带滚轮的三键鼠标 "

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:10
msgid "NDOF Devices (also known as *3D Mouse*)"
msgstr "NDOF 设备 (也叫 *3D 鼠标*)"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:11
msgid "Graphic Tablets"
msgstr "绘画板"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:15
msgid "Usage of Mouse Buttons"
msgstr "鼠标按钮的用法"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:17
msgid ""
"In Blender the :kbd:`RMB` (Right Mouse Button) is generally used for "
"Selection and the :kbd:`LMB` (Left Mouse Button) initiates or confirms "
"actions."
msgstr "在Blender的工作中鼠标占据了很重要的作用。因此我们制定了鼠标按钮在大部分情况下的一般用法："

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:20
msgid "The mouse usage summarized:"
msgstr "鼠标按钮的用法"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:25
msgid ":kbd:`RMB`"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:26
msgid "To select an item"
msgstr "选择一个项目"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:27
msgid ":kbd:`Shift-RMB`"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:28
msgid "To add more items to the selection"
msgstr "添加更多选择"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:29
msgid ":kbd:`LMB`"
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:30
msgid "to perform an action on the selection"
msgstr "接受或确定一个命令"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:32
msgid ""
"Video: `Learn more about Blender's Mouse Button usage "
"<http://vimeo.com/76335056>`_"
msgstr "视频: `学习更多Blender的鼠标键用法 <http://vimeo.com/76335056>`_"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:36
msgid "Exceptions from the Rule"
msgstr "例外情况"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:38
msgid ""
"There are a few corner cases where :kbd:`LMB` is used for selection. For "
"example, the *File Selector*."
msgstr "有些地方， :kbd:`LMB` 是用来选择的。比如 *文件选择* 。"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:43
msgid "Non English Keyboard"
msgstr "非英语键盘"

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:45
msgid ""
"If you use a keyboard with a non-english keyboard layout, you still may "
"benefit from switching your computer to the UK or US layout as long as you "
"work with Blender."
msgstr "如果你使用的不是标准的英式键盘布局, 你也许需要为你的Blender更改为标准的英式键盘或美式键盘布局. "

#: ..\..\interface\input_devices.rst:50
msgid ""
"You can also change the default keymap and default hotkeys from the "
":doc:`User Preferences </preferences/input>`, however this manual assumes "
"you are using the default keymap. :doc:`Read more about Blender "
"configuration </preferences/input>`"
msgstr "注意你也可以改变Blender的默认键盘布局和默认热键. 然而这本手册是基于默认的键盘布局（keymap）编写的."
